 -- Function: turtle.reset ()
     Delete the turtle's drawings from the screen, re-center the turtle
     and set variables to the default values.

         >>> turtle.goto(0,-22)
         >>> turtle.left(100)
         >>> turtle.position()
         (0.00,-22.00)
         >>> turtle.heading()
         100.0
         >>> turtle.reset()
         >>> turtle.position()
         (0.00,0.00)
         >>> turtle.heading()
         0.0



